    "source_html": "<h4>Download SQuAD and Convert to SFT Format</h4>\n<p>We use the <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/rajpurkar/squad\">SQuAD</a> dataset and convert it to prompt/completion JSONL.</p>\n"
